I"<p>I am a Research Assistant Professor in the <a href="https://ocean-sciences.rsmas.miami.edu/index.html">Department of Ocean Sciences</a> at the <a href="http://rsmas.miami.edu">Rosenstiel School of Marine and Atmospheric Science</a> of <a href="http://www.miami.edu">the University of Miami</a>.</p>

<p>I conduct research in physical oceanography, and specifically in atmosphere-ocean interactions, oceanic surface boundary layer dynamics, meridional overturning circulation dynamics, and Agulhas Current System dynamics. I am interested in the nature of oceanic and atmospheric observations, and more generally in time series and covariance analyses of environmental data.</p>

